          <h5 class="card-title">Food & Fun</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Development of a hotel website showcasing services and menu offerings.</p>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Backend Developer</p>
          <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB</p>
          <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Apr 2024 - May 2024</p>
          <a href="https://food-fun-main-2jdm.onrender.com/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary mt-auto" target="_blank">Visit Project</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wanderlust Project Card -->
      <div class="card col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
